308
00:33:28.028 --> 00:33:42.670
<v Maya>It's the idea that the core learning happens on the device. Your smart glasses learn your personal habits, but that raw, sensitive data stays on the glasses. It doesn't get uploaded to a central meta server. The only thing that gets sent back to the mothership is a</v>

