00:33:42.710 --> 00:33:50.799
<v Maya>generic anonymized update like a mathematical adjustment that helps the global model improve without ever sharing your specific raw data.</v>

310
00:33:51.399 --> 00:33:54.042
<v Daniel>So my secrets stay in my pocket, not on a server somewhere.</v>

311
00:33:54.122 --> 00:33:58.827
<v Maya>That's the promise. But it's a promise we as users have to be vigilant about holding them to.</v>

312
00:33:59.107 --> 00:34:07.788
